visual.name: LinearGaugeByMAQSoftware
visual.description: Create at-a-glance visualization to compare your progress against identified goals and warning zones. By allowing you to include multiple data points, the component provides the ability to illustrate trend details, such as monthly or year-to-date completion rates. The pointer notes targets and the colored bar shows the current progress toward those goals.

ChartOrientation.description: Option to update orientation of the visual

Orientation.description: Option to update orientation of the visual

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for scale labels

MinRangeValue.description: Option to provide minimum value of target range

MaxRangeValue.description: Option to provide maximum value of target range

RangeTicksColor.description: Option to provide color of minimum and maximum value ticks

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family for scale labels

fillOption.description: Background fill based on values or percentage

colorOption.description: Color fill based on solidcolor or Gradientcolor

Zone1.description: Option to set color of zone 1

Zone2.description: Option to set color of zone 2

Zone3.description: Option to set color of zone 3

Zone4.description: Option to set color of zone 4

area1.description: Option to set color of zone 1

area2.description: Option to set color of zone 1

area3.description: Option to set color of zone 1

fontFamily.description: Select the font-family of Actual value
Select the font-family of trend labels
Select the font-family of percentage label
